@Source_HostAddress = http://localhost:5282

### Single-name handler: claimed by AlarmTriggeredHandler (first link)
POST {{Source_HostAddress}}/messages/AlarmTriggered

### Single-name handler: passes two links, claimed by AlarmStoppedHandler
POST {{Source_HostAddress}}/messages/AlarmStopped

### Single-name handler with a payload (?payload= binds to Message.Payload)
POST {{Source_HostAddress}}/messages/AlarmPaused?payload=snooze-5min

### Multi-name handler: SomeMultiHandler owns Foo / Bar / Baz
POST {{Source_HostAddress}}/messages/Foo

### Multi-name handler: same handler, different name
POST {{Source_HostAddress}}/messages/Baz?payload=hello

### Unknown name: falls off the end of the chain, nothing handles it
POST {{Source_HostAddress}}/messages/Unknown
